                    p1_6: "<b>1.6</b> Actions aimed at destabilizing server operation, as well as spreading provocative topics, inciting conflicts, or sowing discord are prohibited.",
                    p1_7: "<b>1.7</b> A player must adhere to constructive and respectful communication norms, maintain adequate and consistent gameplay, understand the server concept, and be aware that everything happening is a game. Insults, derogatory statements, bullying, harassment, and any form of discrimination, as well as personal attacks, are prohibited.",
                    p1_8: "<b>1.8</b> The use of any software, exploits, bugs, or other methods that provide an unfair advantage in gameplay is prohibited.",
                    p1_9: "<b>1.9</b> Mass placement of blocks, chiseled blocks/voxels, water, lava, and/or other liquids without purpose, or with the purpose of hindering other players' gameplay and/or circumventing server rules, is prohibited.",
